*   **[[Draft Verein Statutes (English)>>https://github.com/robertschaub/FactHarbor/blob/main/Docs/Legal/DRAFT_Vereinsstatuten_FactHarbor_EN.md]]**

== 4. Intellectual Property & Privacy ==

Detailed legal policies for day-to-day operations are maintained in dedicated documents:

*   **[[Open Source Model & Licensing>>FactHarbor.Organisation.Legal and Compliance.Open Source Model and Licensing.WebHome]]**: Covers code (MIT/AGPL) and documentation (CC BY-SA).
*   **[[Privacy Policy>>FactHarbor.Organisation.Legal and Compliance.Privacy-Policy]]**: Compliance with Swiss FADP and EU GDPR.
*   **[[Transparency Policy>>FactHarbor.Organisation.Legal and Compliance.Transparency-Policy]]**: Our commitment to open finances and decision-making.

